= Aachen, Germany =
[[File:IPT.png|300px|thumb|right|OpenSPIM with temperature controlled sample chamber by Fraunhofer IPT]]
* [http://www.ipt.fraunhofer.de/en/Businessunits/LifeSciencesEngineering.html Life Sciences Engineering Business Unit] at the Fraunhofer Institute for Production Technology IPT.
