= Heidelberg, Germany =
[[File:COS HD OpenSPIM 1.JPG|300px|thumb|right|COS Heidelberg OpenSPIM]]
* [http://www.cos.uni-heidelberg.de/index.php/a.maizel?l=_e Maizel] and [http://www.cos.uni-heidelberg.de/index.php/s.lemke?l=_e Lemke] groups at the [http://www.cos.uni-heidelberg.de/?l=_e Center for Organismal Studies] of the Heidelberg University.
* This setup slightly differs from the specifications of OpenSPIM v1.0. In particular we use a  [http://www.cobolt.se/mld488nm.html Cobolt laser], Nikon lenses and an [http://www.hamamatsucameras.com/flash4/l Orca4], the whole running under Windows7 Pro.
