= Cambridge, UK =
[[File:FirstVolvoxProjection.jpg|300px|thumb|right|<i>Volvox carteri</i> colony imaged with the Goldstein lab OpenSPIM]]
* The [http://www.damtp.cam.ac.uk/user/gold/?l=_e Goldstein] group in the [http://www.damtp.cam.ac.uk/?l=_e Department of Applied Mathematics and Theoretical Physics] at the University of Cambridge. 
* We used a periscope to divert existing green and blue laser lines, and included a Thorlabs [http://www.thorlabs.de/NewGroupPage9.cfm?ObjectGroup_ID=927?l shutter] in the beam path. We also use a Photometrics [http://www.photometrics.com/products/ccdcams/coolsnap-myo.php:l  Coolsnap Myo]. 
