= Melbourne, Australia =
* The Petrou group at the [http://http://www.florey.edu.au/research/ion-channels-disease?l=_e Florey Institute] and [http://www.cfne.unimelb.edu.au/research-laboratories/neurobiology/?i=_e Centre for Neural Engineering] at the University of Melbourne. 
* We are deploying OpenSPIM for CLARITY and Scaleview based imaging of brain tissue for studying neural morphology.  We use Dragon Lasers and a Andor Neo sCMOS camera.
